<H2>Other Activities</H2>
<ul>
<li> Adjunct Professor at the <A HREF="http://math.ipm.ac.ir/vision/index.html">Computer Vision Group, IPM, Iran</a>
<li> Associate Editor of <A HREF="http://scitation.aip.org/IET-CVI">IET Computer Vision</a> 
<li> Associate Editor of <A HREF="http://www.paaonline.net">Pattern Analysis and Applications</a> 
<li> Advisory Editor of <A HREF="http://www.scientiairanica.ir">Scientia Iranica</a> 
<li> Guest Editor: <ul> 
<li><A HREF="http://ijdar.cfar.umd.edu/">IJDAR</a> <A HREF="http://www.cs.bris.ac.uk/~majid/SI-IJDAR/SI-IJDAR04.html">Special Issue</a></b></font> &nbsp;  
<li> <A HREF="http://www.cs.bris.ac.uk/Events/BMVC2000/IVCissue.html">Special Issue of IVC journal on BMVC2000</a>
</ul>
<li> Chairman of the <A HREF="http://www.bmva.ac.uk/">British Machine Vision Association</a> 2005-2008
<li> Steering Committee member of the Medical Image Understanding and Analysis conference <A HREF="http://www.miua.org.uk/">miua.org</a> 2005-2009
<li> Publicity Officer of the <A HREF="http://www.bmva.ac.uk/">British Machine Vision Association</a> (2000-2005)
<li> Member of <A HREF="http://www.iasted.com/">IASTED</a> Technical Committee on Image Processing (2000-2004)
<li> Chair and Organiser: <A HREF="http://www.cs.bris.ac.uk/%7Emiua05/index.html">MIUA2005</A>
<li> Co-Chair and Co-Organiser: <A HREF="http://conferences.iee.org/vie2005/">VIE2005</A> &nbsp; <A HREF="http://www.cs.bris.ac.uk/Events/CPA2001/">CPA2001</A> &nbsp; <A HREF="http://www.cs.bris.ac.uk/Events/CAAUK2001/">CAAUK2001</A> &nbsp;  <A HREF="http://www.cs.bris.ac.uk/Events/BMVC2000/">BMVC2000</A>
<li> Tutorial and Demos Chair: <A HREF="http://www.icapr2005.org.uk/">ICAPR 2005</A>
<li> Publicity Chair: <A href="http://www.fg2006.ecs.soton.ac.uk/">FG2006</a> &nbsp; <A HREF="http://www.ee.surrey.ac.uk/icpr04/">ICPR04</A> 
<li> <A HREF="pcactivity.html">Program Committees</a>
<li> <A HREF="http://www.bmva.ac.uk/">BMVA</A> Technical Meeting Chair/Co-Chair on 1- <A HREF="http://www.bmva.ac.uk/meetings/meetings/99/1Dec99/index.html">   Industrial Inspection</a> 2- <A HREF="http://www.bmva.ac.uk/meetings/meetings/old/meeting-1997-05-08.html"> Optimisation Issues in Computer Vision</FONT></a> 3- <A HREF="http://www.bmva.ac.uk/meetings/">Document and Text Recognition in Images and Video Sequences</a>. <br>
<li> Member of <A HREF="http://www.epsrc.ac.uk">EPSRC</a> College (2006-09), 
<A HREF="http://www.iet.org.uk">IET</a>, and Senior Member of <A HREF="http://www.ieee.org">IEEE</a>.
